OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFrequent
OL,6,Fshowers will continue through the
OL,7,Fevening but will clear slowly from the
OL,8,Feast overnight, these will be wintry
OL,9,Fover the hills. It will become cold as
OL,10,Fclear spells increase.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FBright morning, a few
OL,13,Fshowers west. Cloud spreads north with
OL,14,Frain soon following. This heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent with snow to low levels.
OL,16,FThe wind strengthens to severe gale
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
