OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and severe gales clear
OL,7,FSunday morning, leaving a few showers.
OL,8,FMostly dry but cloudy Monday and
OL,9,FTuesday though some patchy rain at
OL,10,Ftimes.
